  "title": "Structural analysis of cancer-relevant TCR-CD3 and peptide-MHC complexes by cryoEM.",
  "journal": "Nature communications",
  "year": 2023,
  "authors": "Saotome K, Dudgeon D, Colotti K, Moore MJ, Jones J, Zhou Y, Rafique A, Yancopoulos GD, Murphy AJ, Lin JC, Olson WC, Franklin MC."
